name: Skunk - A New Breed Of Weed - An Eighth (3.5g)
description:
A new breed of weed!

	An aromatic herbal blend, when burned releases a sweet fruity aroma.

	This is the best alternative to weed – so good we actually think its better.

	Order now and get it with a free promotional tin (for a limited time only)!

	A very giggly and strong head high, only small quantities are required. Very potent.

	Effects-
When smoked in a spliff or bong effects come on within 5 minutes. Result is a very strong head and body stone with trippy elements when smoked in high doses that lasts up to 1 hour and a half, this product is very potent and as a result the recommended starting dose is 100mg.

	Not to be purchased by anyone under the age of 18, sold as room incense only, not for human consumption.

name: Spice Gold An Eighth (3g)
description:
The premium Spice blend. Packed in high quality re-sealable pouches to ensure freshness.

	Spice is an exotic blend that releases a rich aroma when burned.
The plants contained in Spice have been used ritually by ancient cultures throughout the world. Spice releases a pleasing aroma that is acceptable anywhere, anytime. It is perfect whilst chilling out at home or with friends. Packaged in a high quality re-sealable pouch to ensure freshness.

	Effects-
Strong stoned effect verging on trippy. Duration of high- up to 8 hours (very long lasting) recommended dosage – roughly 400mg, best smoked in a joint or in a bong.

	Ingredients:
Baybean, Blue Lotus, Lion’s Tail, Lousewort, Indian Warrior, Dwarf Scullcap, Maconha Brava, Pink Lotus, Marshmallow, Red Clover, Rose, Siberian Motherwort, Vanilla and Honey

	Use Responsibly:
Not permitted for sale to persons under the age of 18
